Interface ClassifiableVectorial

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Classifiable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GraphicLayer, VectorLayer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultGraphicLayer, FLyrVect, FLyrVect, MapSheetsGrid

    public interface ClassifiableVectorial
extends Classifiable

    All vector layers that can be classifiable and can have associated a legend, must implement ClassifiableVectorial.
